## 📋 القواعد الإلزامية

### 1. **Backend Standards**

#### Structure:
```
- استخدم NestJS modules pattern
- كل feature في مجلد منفصل
- DTOs منفصلة عن Entities
- Services تحتوي على Business Logic فقط
- Controllers تحتوي على HTTP handling فقط
```

#### Naming Conventions:
```typescript
// Files
- *.module.ts
- *.controller.ts
- *.service.ts
- *.dto.ts
- *.entity.ts (إذا لزم)

// Classes
- PascalCase: AuthService, CasesController
- Interfaces: IAuthService, ICaseRepository

// Functions
- camelCase: createCase, validateUser
```

#### Multi-Tenancy (الأهم!):
```typescript
// ✅ ALWAYS include tenantId in queries
const cases = await this.prisma.case.findMany({
  where: { tenantId: user.tenantId } // مهم جداً!
});

// ❌ NEVER query without tenantId
const cases = await this.prisma.case.findMany(); // خطأ!

// ✅ ALWAYS use @TenantId() decorator
@Get()
async findAll(@TenantId() tenantId: string) {
  return this.casesService.findAll(tenantId);
}
```

#### DTOs:
```typescript
// ✅ ALWAYS use class-validator
export class CreateCaseDto {
  @IsString()
  @IsNotEmpty()
  title: string;

  @IsEnum(CaseType)
  caseType: CaseType;
  
  @IsOptional()
  @IsString()
  description?: string;
}

// ✅ ALWAYS use @ApiProperty for Swagger
@ApiProperty({ example: 'قضية رقم 123' })
title: string;
```

#### Error Handling:
```typescript
// ✅ Use built-in NestJS exceptions
throw new NotFoundException('Case not found');
throw new BadRequestException('Invalid data');
throw new UnauthorizedException('Invalid credentials');

// ❌ Don't use generic errors
throw new Error('Something went wrong'); // خطأ!
```

