## ✅ Best Practices - التزم بها!

### Performance:
```typescript
// ✅ Use indexes
@@index([tenantId, caseNumber])

// ✅ Use select to limit fields
select: { id: true, title: true }

// ✅ Use pagination
take: 10, skip: page * 10

// ✅ Avoid N+1 queries
include: { client: true } // instead of separate query
```

### Security:
```typescript
// ✅ Validate all input
@IsString() @IsNotEmpty()

// ✅ Sanitize output
delete user.password;

// ✅ Use environment variables
process.env.JWT_SECRET

// ✅ Rate limiting (in main.ts)
app.use(rateLimit({ windowMs: 15 * 60 * 1000, max: 100 }));
```

### Maintainability:
```typescript
// ✅ Descriptive names
getUserCases() // not getData()

// ✅ Consistent formatting
// Use Prettier

// ✅ Meaningful commits
"feat: add case creation endpoint"
"fix: tenant isolation in cases query"

// ✅ Documentation
// README.md with setup instructions
// API docs with Swagger
```

